/show/110077.A_Pair_of_Blue_Eyes\" title=\"A Pair of Blue Eyes\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eA Pair of Blue Eyes\u003c/a\u003e in 1873. In the novel, Hardy chose to leave one of his protagonists, Knight, literally hanging off a cliff staring into the stony eyes of a trilobite embedded in the rock that has been dead for millions of years. This became the archetypal — and literal — cliff-hanger of Victorian prose.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003ci\u003eExcerpted from \u003ca href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thomas_Hardy\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eWikipedia\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/i\u003e","isGrAuthor":false,"works":{"__typename":"ContributorWorksConnection","totalCount":1201},"profileImageUrl":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/authors/1429946281i/15905._UX200_CR0,0,200,200_.jpg","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/15905.Thomas_Hardy","user":null,"viewerIsFollowing":null,"followers":{"__typename":"ContributorFollowersConnection","totalCount":5196}},"Contributor:kca://author/amzn1.gr.author.v1.QN54WbQx3VA3USWOay0drw":{"id":"kca://author/amzn1.gr.author.v1.QN54WbQx3VA3USWOay0drw","__typename":"Contributor","name":"Alexander Theroux","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/93847.Alexander_Theroux","isGrAuthor":false},"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.98uEhZa2ToBt3ERweEMzyQ":{"id":"kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.98uEhZa2ToBt3ERweEMzyQ","__typename":"Book","legacyId":32650,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/32650.The_Return_of_the_Native","title":"The Return of the Native","titleComplete":"The Return of the Native","description":"Tempestuous Eustacia Vye passes her days dreaming of passionate love and the escape it may bring from the small community of Egdon Heath. Hearing that Clym Yeobright is to return from Paris, she sets her heart on marrying him, believing that through him she can leave rural life and find fulfilment elsewhere. But she is to be disappointed, for Clym has dreams of his own, and th